                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Strength training (Upper body - chest, shoulders, arms)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Light cardio (Brisk walking, cycling) & Mobility exercises</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Strength training (Lower body - legs, glutes, calves)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Yoga or stretching for flexibility</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Full-body resistance training (Functional strength exercises)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Light swimming or recreational activity</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
